      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this reliable daily driver that's ready for its next chapter! It's in honest, fair condition, showing some expected character and wear from its time on the road, but it still has plenty of life left to give. If you're looking for a dependable vehicle that gets the job done without the premium price tag, this is the one for you!",
